## add-signalargh

# Add SignalArgh Command

## TRIGGER
"add signalargh", "use signalargh", "add signalr"

## PURPOSE
Integrates SignalArgh real-time messaging - free, no-registration SignalR hub for JavaScript, Python, or C# projects.

## WHAT IT DOES
- Detects project language (JS/Python/C#)
- Prompts for: Channel ID, User ID strategy, Features needed
- Creates: SignalR client helper file with complete implementation
- Supports: Channels, Groups, Announcements, Auto-reconnect

## FULL IMPLEMENTATION
When trigger detected, read complete implementation:
```powershell
$content = Get-Content "C:/Users/mike.ullman/OneDrive - Vizio, Inc/Documents/Cline/Rules/full/add-signalargh.md" -Raw
```

Or use read_file tool:
`full/add-signalargh.md`

## QUICK REFERENCE
- **Hub URL:** https://signalargh.mikesendpoint.com/hub
- **No Auth:** Just channelId + userId query params
- **Channel Isolation:** Messages never cross channels
- **Auto-Reconnect:** Built-in reconnection on connection loss
- **Multi-Language:** JavaScript (browser/Node), Python, C#


